main event: A witness observed a bright green light moving erratically in the sky over Cloquet, Minnesota on January 3, 1962.
interesting points: The object was described as a green-colored light, size of a baseball., The observation lasted for about 10 minutes., The object appeared to be at high altitude and moved in an erratic course., This sighting aligns with other reported observations in the same area on the same date., There were no other confirmed witnesses reported for this sighting.
